  "title": "6 Months Locum Pharmacy Technician (Islandwide / Flexi Office Hours) #HGNT",
  "description": "<p>We are hiring 6 Months Locum Pharmacy Technician<strong> </strong>to be outsourced to our clients from reputable healthcare organizations.</p><p>Apply now!</p><p>Job Responsibilities</p><ul><li>Processes prescriptions and dispenses medications to polyclinic patients in accordance with doctor’s directions as specified in prescriptions</li><li>Supports Medication Delivery Service (MDS) and PILBOX service for remote collection of medications</li><li>Provides Tele-dispensing services (where applicable)</li><li>Assists in video consultation (VC) and medication reconciliation</li></ul><p>Job Requirements:</p><ul><li>GCE ‘O’ Level with a Certificate in Pharmacy Technician Course or Diploma in Pharmaecutical Science </li><li>Able to float around different locations </li></ul><p>All Interested candidates are invited to email your resume in MS Word format to:<br />\nhealthcare8@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>\nPlease include your full working experience, education background, notice period, expected salary.</p><p>Siow Hui Hui (Anthea)</p><p>Outsourcing Team</p><p>Ref Code: #HGNT</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p><p>Company Reg. No. 199601303W| EA License Number: 99C4599<br />\nWe regret to inform that only suitable candidates will be shortlisted for an interview</p>",
